gavl
------------------------------------------
Library for handling uncompressed audio and video data

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libgavl-devel-1.4.0-1bl1
  libgavl1-1.4.0-1bl1
  libgdither1-0.6-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.5-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libgdither-devel-0.6-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/gmerlin/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/gmerlin/gavl-1.4.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gavl-1.4.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gavl-1.4.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gavl-1.4.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gavl-1.4.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgavl1-1.4.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgavl-devel-1.4.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(gavl)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/gavl.README
  /usr/share/doc/gavl/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/gavl/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/gavl/README
  /usr/share/doc/gavl/TODO

(libgavl1)
  /usr/bin/cyggavl-1.dll

(libgavl-devel)
  /usr/include/gavl/compression.h
  /usr/include/gavl/gavl.h
  /usr/include/gavl/gavl_version.h
  /usr/include/gavl/gavldefs.h
  /usr/include/gavl/gavldsp.h
  /usr/include/gavl/gavltime.h
  /usr/include/gavl/metadata.h
  /usr/include/gavl/metatags.h
  /usr/include/gavl/timecode.h
  /usr/lib/libgavl.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/gavl.pc

